claim.claim-text:
1. A method for growing plants in a heated environment, the method comprising:
providing a building structure having heating equipment;
venting heat from said heating equipment to an external environment wherein vented heat is waste heat from said building structure;
extracting said vented heat in a radiant manner during said venting step, wherein said extracting is performed with heat exchange tubes wrapped around said heating equipment and wherein said extracting is performed with a food grade heat transfer fluid other than water;
supplying said radiant heat to a greenhouse on a rooftop; and
providing a growing environment in said greenhouse to grow plants.
